Enum UiMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<UiMessages>
      • io.elegie.luchess.web.launcher.ui.UiMessages
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UiMessages>

    public enum UiMessages
extends java.lang.Enum<UiMessages>
    All messages used by the application. The value of each message is the key to be used in the bundle files.
